description: Bob Jo Truck strives to provide our customers a new spin on Korean cuisine that’s healthy and delicious because we only use fresh organic ingredients prepared daily in a clean environment. We utilize our mobility to offer fast and convenient service for our busy urbanite customers who crave good food but don’t have time to waste. Wherever there is food injustice, you will find us…Wherever there is suffering, we’ll be there…We are ‘BOBJO!”
name: Bob Jo Truck
